2143
02:17:47,550 --> 02:17:54,056
Are you sure?

2144
02:17:55,725 --> 02:17:57,393
Or are you blind?

2145
02:18:00,981 --> 02:18:02,314
All right.

2146
02:18:05,694 --> 02:18:07,319
Um....

