2411
02:35:41,749 --> 02:35:43,499
No, pyramids. Pyramids. Pyramids.

2412
02:35:43,667 --> 02:35:46,085
[SPEAKING IN ARABIC]

2413
02:35:48,213 --> 02:35:49,922
-Pyramids?
