2436
02:38:23,660 --> 02:38:26,162
...and felt like a complete human being.

2437
02:38:30,209 --> 02:38:32,210
[SPEAKING IN ARABIC]

2438
02:38:46,350 --> 02:38:48,935
MALCOLM: Now, you may be shocked
